  "description": {
   "en": "“In exchange for a few years of your life, I can help you forget everything about a person,” this was her offer that attracted dozens to her. All of which offered up years of their lives in exchange for a peace of mind. From memories about an imperial concubine’s hairpin, to memories of a cultivator’s magical sword; every memory hid a deeper truth, a more painful truth.\n\n“Say, do you have anyone you’d like to forget?”\n\n“I do, but I’ve already forgotten.”\n\n---\n**Alternate Raw:** [AC.QQ](https://ac.qq.com/Comic/comicInfo/id/639919), [iQiyi Manhua](https://www.iqiyi.com/manhua/detail_18yzm972cl.html), [U17](https://www.u17.com/comic/182884.html), [Yizhikan](https://www.yizhikan.com/comic/13030), [Zymk](https://www.zymk.cn/3669/)\n**Official Translations:** [English (Webcomics)](https://www.webcomicsapp.com/comic/5dc271148c252b053a3b6896), [English (Flying Lines)](https://www.flying-lines.com/comic/memory-erasing-bell)\nOfficial Animated Version: [Ake Animation on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLokmx9AcsdTfyWucgbtnaHVp1sdvfoQsJ)  \nOfficial Subtitled Version: [S1](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo11RdjLkdJCnxPC3o10Syk53nsqBhJk_)"
